1. Technical Overview

The NBHCA Revenue Engine will be a modular, Laravel-based web application designed to manage ticket sales, Stripe payment processing, attendee validation, and event revenue analytics.

The system will:

Operate as a standalone Laravel application

Integrate with the existing NBHCA website

Sync with the bespoke CRM system

Use Stripe for secure payment processing

Be deployed on a secure VPS environment (UK region for GDPR compliance)

