4.5 Stripe Integration
4.5.1 Stripe Checkout Flow

User selects ticket(s)

Server creates Stripe Checkout Session

User redirected to Stripe

Stripe processes payment

Stripe sends webhook

System verifies webhook signature

Order record created

Tickets generated

Confirmation email triggered

Required Stripe Webhooks:

checkout.session.completed

payment_intent.succeeded

payment_intent.payment_failed

charge.refunded

Webhook verification must use Stripe signature validation.

No card details stored locally.

4.6 QR Code Generation

Use server-side QR library (e.g., Simple QR Code package)

Encode ticket UUID

Store QR as SVG or PNG

Attach to PDF ticket

4.7 PDF Ticket Generation

